&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll try running it a dozen times to make sure there&apos;s no race condition anymore. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15245757" author="ifesdjeen" created="Mon, 18 Apr 2016 14:35:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jkni&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jkni&quot;&gt;jkni&lt;/a&gt; I&apos;ve ran the dtest 2 x 30 times (isolated &lt;tt&gt;NativeTransportTest&lt;/tt&gt; although), it passed all times. Could you take a look at patch?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15246415" author="jkni" created="Mon, 18 Apr 2016 19:57:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch looks good to me and your explanation makes sense. I can also confirm that I can no longer reproduce the failures on my machine. Can you do full unit test/dtests runs and then I&apos;ll +1 for merge? Just want to make sure there aren&apos;t any unexpected consequences.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
